      desc "macchanger is a utility for viewing or manipulating the MACs of NICs.

macchanger is a GNU/Linux utility for viewing and
manipulating the MAC addresses of network interfaces.
It can set specific, random, vendor-based 
(with a 6000+ vendor list), and device-type-based MACs.
"
